; Coverage test for draft.cc lines 457-469: @ per-unit cost handling
; When a draft template posting has a cost with the @ operator,
; the code unrounds the cost, multiplies it by the amount, and
; preserves the commodity. Exercises:
;   L457: if (post.cost) -- entering cost handling
;   L458: if (post.cost->sign() < 0) -- false branch (positive cost)
;   L461: post.cost->in_place_unround()
;   L463: if (*post.cost_operator == "@") -- true branch
;   L467-469: cost multiplication and commodity preservation
;   L474-476: new_post->cost = *post.cost

2024/01/01 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food    10 AAPL @ $5.00
    Assets:Cash   $-50.00

test xact 2024/06/15 Grocery to Expenses:Food '@' '$6.00' '10 AAPL' from Assets:Cash
2024/06/15 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food                            10 AAPL
    Assets:Cash
end test
